docs.lead_paragraph: Elon Musk is on the brink. In an emotional, hourlong interview with The New York Times, Mr. Musk, the chief executive of Tesla and SpaceX, described what he called the most difficult year of his career. Over the last 16 months, he has gone from seemingly on top of the world to facing one of the most intense existential crises of his entrepreneurial career.

headline.main: Elon Musk’s No Good, Very Bad Year: A Tesla Timeline
headline.print_headline: Timeline of Turmoil For Tesla’s Chief
